{"tid":59913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最記得自己發過咩夢","createTime":"2016-12-30T05:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T07:27:28.000Z","uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6a8a69b85b1a13d4de279db9ea64a68451bd26","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日發啲九唔撘八嘅夢 咩返左間學校水浸出唔返嚟要玩遊戲贏左先得 又有去去下宜家傢私行過一條街去左海洋公園<br />\n之前發過一啲係同嘈左交嘅朋友 ex呀傾返計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有惡夢 不停同其他人跳樓 但唔係跳死左 係不斷跳完跑返上樓再跳 同埋另一個係係夢入面訓著 再醒返個時身邊嘅人死晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時仲會發春夢"},{"pid":"ef295b8d27b50d60c81ec969c917f5758b99a705","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"入嚟講低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571561f4888c25cf6e7b0c36e8bf44b32603c8e9","tid":59913,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢婆婆喺鄉下間屋度<br />\n我行上二樓<br />\n見到佢背對住我食緊飯<br />\n枱上面有四五碟餸但得佢自己食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d870e4f8b7b3b8b7b83903249674f669528b7685","tid":59913,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"發夢見番鍾意過幾年嘅女仔，同佢一齊去另一個地方<br />\n一方面好想繼續個旅程，個女仔都好願意咁，但自己覺得對唔住女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現實係同個女仔已經冇聯絡，因為一啲事甚至對佢幾反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好愛而家個女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75ab7a909e570671f3fca34ae4af705d95b0f20","tid":59913,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"岩岩尋晚發完詠春打MMA，重要大混戰6人對打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨訓岩岩睇緊葉問3片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一次係揸波子抄360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n清醒夢果次控制到夢中秘書性高潮，太興奮想去屌佢就直接醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發夢都無閪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重要清醒夢"},{"pid":"464579a655a64a5dcf1f179ea8a582ba073e543a","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢婆婆喺鄉下間屋度<br />\n我行上二樓<br />\n見到佢背對住我食緊飯<br />\n枱上面有四五碟餸但得佢自己食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都叫淫<br />\n<br />\n婆婆走左？定好耐冇返去探佢？"},{"pid":"169ced4e1f8474e2350b59b70566c5d18cb5f398","tid":59913,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢婆婆喺鄉下間屋度<br />\n我行上二樓<br />\n見到佢背對住我食緊飯<br />\n枱上面有四五碟餸但得佢自己食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都叫淫<br />\n<br />\n婆婆走左？定好耐冇返去探佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾個月見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知點解會發個噉嘅夢"},{"pid":"762a56fab3027fdbf3eb5d7c5d06f8608a6e4b3e","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:19:05.000Z","msg":