\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你平時成日唔開心？"},{"pid":"34a26eb9e57550fcfaaddb0a033cad9e953799d9","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係西西里右頸中槍, 原完唔痛, 癱左一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中完槍即刻醒？定係夢到等醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bb351fd2541155182b757a8b47f155ac6cf7c","tid":59913,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"同女神好爽皮地拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後一醒左發現自已流左幾滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4cb6fc85bce9d27cbe2f5d7a3b3258d6c87d0f","tid":59913,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce180f163bf07b7a71b0b28f415db7685fdcc97e","tid":59913,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"細細個發惡夢嗰陣，夢見我老竇揸住把刀斬我，到咗大個都好記得，童年陰影。<br />\n<br />\n因為嗰陣睇到單新聞話，大陸有條變態佬斬咗個五歲細佬仔嚟食，我就無啦啦開始覺得老竇係食人族。"},{"pid":"bc3ab26a5ef875a356a0c11cba17c9decd796d78","tid":59913,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個發惡夢嗰陣，夢見我老竇揸住把刀斬我，到咗大個都好記得，童年陰影。<br />\n<br />\n因為嗰陣睇到單新聞話，大陸有條變態佬斬咗個五歲細佬仔嚟食，我就無啦啦開始覺得老竇係食人族。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n令尊好慘 無端端比個仔當變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6373acdf95dbc7c700ad7ce6e63259e847f2ac2","tid":59913,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發夢見番鍾意過幾年嘅女仔，同佢一齊去另一個地方<br />\n一方面好想繼續個旅程，個女仔都好願意咁，但自己覺得對唔住女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現實係同個女仔已經冇聯絡，因為一啲事甚至對佢幾反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好愛而家個女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夢呢啲嘢唔一定代表你宜家諗緊咩嘅 無須自責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續愛你宜家個女朋友啦 祝幸福</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<br />\n以前無諗過會搵到個愛自己嘅人 一定會好好錫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f66228e3ba12e82a47192c516d20f4f6b8d8912","tid":59913,"uid":6767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"由細到大經常發同一個夢<br />\n夢見自己係一條好窄既巷跑緊 <br />\n遠處發緊光但睇唔到有咩 次次都跑唔到去盡頭就醒左<br />\n沿路條巷兩邊都落晒閘 但有啲恐怖手會開閘伸手出黎想捉我<br />\n個夢發左應該8年左右<br />\n<br />\n直到有一次發夢 我終於跑到盡頭 <br />\n係發光果到見到我媽成個天使咁等緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就無再發過相同既夢 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db34ff21161c085c685cb83f5b81691152a86e3a","tid":59913,"uid":60746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"去日本旅行撞到上原亞衣，成功約炮，結果就扑嗰時俾我呀哥嘈醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5446cb7b39e553a0cb0fe1785e3f29eda63b9934","tid":59913,"uid":38167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"前日夢見男朋友係屯門等我，我係元朗上左架64k，話下個站就到，點知下個站去左金巴利道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (明明架車係去大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，我仲心諗: 屌搭錯左對面線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落車見到the one,  我覺得搭lift落到最底就有西鐵搭，點知係咁飛lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就醒左 (現實中我淨係去過the one一兩次，亦唔肯定金巴利道係咪尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔熟路)"},{"pid":"7903fd1f78f54d79392f8384b1c9f25008f331b5","tid":59913,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>世日末日夢/係一個深淵既地方釣魚<br />\n<br />\n同埋平時夢境都係好黑暗陰深，未試過發有陽光既夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你平時成日唔開心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係，會笑，但好似好耐未試過真正開心過"},{"pid":"9f36d64cf150570793ce4f98a93d0f266cd05bab","tid":59913,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"細個行山見到廢屋入面有個神像...<br />\n跟住連續幾日訓教都夢到自己行去間廢屋到....<br />\n仲成日俾鬼壓"},{"pid":"ced2557d819f07f12cf280e173e1eb107f7e2fdd","tid":59913,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢婆婆喺鄉下間屋度<br />\n我行上二樓<br />\n見到佢背對住我食緊飯<br />\n枱上面有四五碟餸但得佢自己食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你婆婆係淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0cde81ca23e91bb82785f29a3a65527335c4c3","tid":59913,"uid":58855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"每次發夢都好似拍戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一次係夢見自己係殺手，揸車係咁避警察，最後發現自己要殺果個人係自己個friend，於是一槍爆自己頭，之後仲見到自己上左天堂然後投胎變左另一個人<br />\n<br />\n另一次係好細個果時發惡夢嚇醒左，之後就同呀媽講，點知呀媽一轉身就係異型，然後又嚇醒左，就咁重覆左三四次先真正醒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ce70b56316290a999bcd418b0a3139f171c452","tid":59913,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女神主動wts我，仲不斷開話題"},{"pid":"938402317c8bbd51fa45b766684eeef93a37bebf","tid":59913,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女神主動wts我，仲不斷開話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7eebe797bc48ac31a25c81099e6a24e5f159ed","tid":59913,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"一個好撚靚仔既男仔彈琴俾我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢望我既眼神令我覺得自己變成左"},{"pid":"81c454e5deffd33e38660a1d04cc2f6555769be5","tid":59913,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個好撚靚仔既男仔彈琴俾我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢望我既眼神令我覺得自己變成左佢既全世界<br />\n真係唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b4cd78c3fff0330b1cbeb19fa6e6e1cb8a032422","tid":59913,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"嗰陣老豆喺我考試嗰陣走咗，我冇機會去醫院探佢、見佢最後一面<br />\n佢走咗之後我好嬲自己，因為喺佢走之前嗰個父親節，我同佢一齊睇父親節廣告，我想同佢講我愛你，我知機會可能不多，但我最後都係冇做到，我一生嘅遺憾就係冇得陪住佢行最後嗰段路同埋唔夠膽表達愛意<br />\n之後過咗一排我發夢見到佢，我即刻攬到佢實一實，係溫暖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心諗居然喺夢到feel到體溫，然後喊醒咗<br />\n之後所有有佢嘅夢我都記得"},{"pid":"6656d718c3f596c2b0c60dc9bb0d206222f04ca6","tid":59913,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢婆婆喺鄉下間屋度<br />\n我行上二樓<br />\n見到佢背對住我食緊飯<br />\n枱上面有四五碟餸但得佢自己食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你婆婆係淫娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為自己好好笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf4ec476e73c773929106c8ff4d55f57a14b513","tid":59913,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰陣老豆喺我考試嗰陣走咗，我冇機會去醫院探佢、見佢最後一面<br />\n佢走咗之後我好嬲自己，因為喺佢走之前嗰個父親節，我同佢一齊睇父親節廣告，我想同佢講我愛你，我知機會可能不多，但我最後都係冇做到，我一生嘅遺憾就係冇得陪住佢行最後嗰段路同埋唔夠膽表達愛意<br />\n之後過咗一排我發夢見到佢，我即刻攬到佢實一實，係溫暖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心諗居然喺夢到feel到體溫，然後喊醒咗<br />\n之後所有有佢嘅夢我都記得</blockquote><br />\n好sad...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09024f79eb4aabb9b0b664bf056f9ba14eff484","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同女神好爽皮地拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後一醒左發現自已流左幾滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假夢真喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好sad"},{"pid":"9d09cd36bfc4e0d7a07fc0d4976dd8a90640a52b","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發燒個陣有條女幫我含醒左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒返先知發緊夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發夢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd40747b96cf6d2d904da3c0c520b9ad628c9824","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個發惡夢嗰陣，夢見我老竇揸住把刀斬我，到咗大個都好記得，童年陰影。<br />\n<br />\n因為嗰陣睇到單新聞話，大陸有條變態佬斬咗個五歲細佬仔嚟食，我就無啦啦開始覺得老竇係食人族。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都試過夢到俾屋企人追殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個夢好短 所以冇乜感覺"},{"pid":"eb267c7c8feba733b3d3f49e3cd3c3bd74ae3956","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大經常發同一個夢<br />\n夢見自己係一條好窄既巷跑緊 <br />\n遠處發緊光但睇唔到有咩 次次都跑唔到去盡頭就醒左<br />\n沿路條巷兩邊都落晒閘 但有啲恐怖手會開閘伸手出黎想捉我<br />\n個夢發左應該8年左右<br />\n<br />\n直到有一次發夢 我終於跑到盡頭 <br />\n係發光果到見到我媽成個天使咁等緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就無再發過相同既夢 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑左八年先到盡頭"},{"pid":"ced9a2f7b09aa66fef92715a1dd0d91be83c7f7a","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本旅行撞到上原亞衣，成功約炮，結果就扑嗰時俾我呀哥嘈醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好慘 有冇屌爆你呀哥"},{"pid":"4f26d4eea27c26df9928a7717c4ff05e20f6caef","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日夢見男朋友係屯門等我，我係元朗上左架64k，話下個站就到，點知下個站去左金巴利道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (明明架車係去大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，我仲心諗: 屌搭錯左對面線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落車見到the one,  我覺得搭lift落到最底就有西鐵搭，點知係咁飛lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就醒左 (現實中我淨係去過the one一兩次，亦唔肯定金巴利道係咪尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔熟路)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 發夢都撘錯車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1842e988308d3d506df8be1dcc011a9e162191ca","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>世日末日夢/係一個深淵既地方釣魚<br />\n<br />\n同埋平時夢境都係好黑暗陰深，未試過發有陽光既夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你平時成日唔開心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係，會笑，但好似好耐未試過真正開心過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兄台 你有冇人生目標"},{"pid":"3c613ce293eb73b81083e11fec00b27b1b572ec2","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個行山見到廢屋入面有個神像...<br />\n跟住連續幾日訓教都夢到自己行去間廢屋到....<br />\n仲成日俾鬼壓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時最慘係第一次發嗰個夢好驚 第二日訓教不停諗住唔好重複發同一個夢 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2791e24fab9ec0edfb8f54981459538a651d57e8","tid":59913,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de0cfa758d506b20537bf121ee8920949fc52203","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次發夢都好似拍戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一次係夢見自己係殺手，揸車係咁避警察，最後發現自己要殺果個人係自己個friend，於是一槍爆自己頭，之後仲見到自己上左天堂然後投胎變左另一個人<br />\n<br />\n另一次係好細個果時發惡夢嚇醒左，之後就同呀媽講，點知呀媽一轉身就係異型，然後又嚇醒左，就咁重覆左三四次先真正醒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二個夢好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdb493c2d78f9ec589d091fae6563391f731a95","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女神主動wts我，仲不斷開話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現實就..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f221c425eb694e125a00df9ba2879022efe287c1","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個好撚靚仔既男仔彈琴俾我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢望我既眼神令我覺得自己變成左佢既全世界<br />\n真係唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲男性嘅眼神真係好正 好有魅力 好吸引 我幻想到 我真係幻想到"},{"pid":"86370954b3c0b5f8c1ee82830fcfb736cdabd500","tid":59913,"uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"屋企有條走廊連去廳<br />\n有次發夢 屋企人開咗兩台麻雀<br />\n唔知點解我凌空飛起比人拉住隻腳入走廊<br />\n 叫救命冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地繼續打麻雀<br />\n而家仲記得飛嗰種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾爽"},{"pid":"c812221515c1e1d11c38b82812a4fa6ca6d17b85","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰陣老豆喺我考試嗰陣走咗，我冇機會去醫院探佢、見佢最後一面<br />\n佢走咗之後我好嬲自己，因為喺佢走之前嗰個父親節，我同佢一齊睇父親節廣告，我想同佢講我愛你，我知機會可能不多，但我最後都係冇做到，我一生嘅遺憾就係冇得陪住佢行最後嗰段路同埋唔夠膽表達愛意<br />\n之後過咗一排我發夢見到佢，我即刻攬到佢實一實，係溫暖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心諗居然喺夢到feel到體溫，然後喊醒咗<br />\n之後所有有佢嘅夢我都記得</blockquote><br />\n好sad...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好耐之前發夢都試過攬住一個我唔可以再攬住嘅人 然後喊醒 嗰日個夢發左好耐 我同佢傾左好耐計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0929495048b2e0d4b3d5ff5a57d817b413c4c45","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蟻多嬲死象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔驚自爆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e556a22299a0fe69bc9f5228f0c3bf9f36d8773d","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企有條走廊連去廳<br />\n有次發夢 屋企人開咗兩台麻雀<br />\n唔知點解我凌空飛起比人拉住隻腳入走廊<br />\n 叫救命冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地繼續打麻雀<br />\n而家仲記得飛嗰種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾爽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我坐過只可以離地半米嘅飛氈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飛左去街市"},{"pid":"28510f78bb30b780e7c73ac23bf54c57ec7f39c0","tid":59913,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個好撚靚仔既男仔彈琴俾我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢望我既眼神令我覺得自己變成左佢既全世界<br />\n真係唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲男性嘅眼神真係好正 好有魅力 好吸引 我幻想到 我真係幻想到</blockquote><br />\n溫柔到我想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜之後再冇夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98a0187a5a8115fcbc34f9cce810eca549bad9e","tid":59913,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你平時成日唔開心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係，會笑，但好似好耐未試過真正開心過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兄台 你有冇人生目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇，成日問自己想點，想搵樣興趣想搵個目標，但始終都唔知自己最想做乜。<br />\n<br />\n點解第二條問題就會問有冇人生目標？係好易睇得出？定係你識解夢"},{"pid":"c563d758db8e8a3b2aaf56aa0b2c45f98da7d782","tid":59913,"uid":10205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4fb6f19b2e656943b92054693f81139209223a7","tid":59913,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"夢見有個好寂寞既絲打開post"},{"pid":"afc3c9a6e4e2536d873a23a0efffa03a5af22e0f","tid":59913,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"同女神扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7bee668c9039d1abb9055f22597adf25d05b40","tid":59913,"uid":48893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"試過夢見有人傷害我身邊既人 唔記得屋企人定女朋友<br />\n跟住我綁架左佢 <br />\n用鉗鉗晒佢手指腳指甲佢<br />\n敲碎晒佢棚牙<br />\n將佢兩粒睾丸用兩支篤魚蛋既牙簽釘係左右兩邊大脾到<br />\n跟住捉埋佢女朋友逼佢含到爆嗰下要條女咬爛佢吞落肚 <br />\n唔係就殺左條女佢<br />\n<br />\n跟住就醒左覺得勁恐怖"},{"pid":"04d0a024f301181c6ef2228a74881cc480e52eb8","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲男性嘅眼神真係好正 好有魅力 好吸引 我幻想到 我真係幻想到</blockquote><br />\n溫柔到我想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜之後再冇夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係未來等緊你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369737449daf475d5c31de6bbb11c9f3810e5551","tid":59913,"uid":58078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得除浴帽就番左學"},{"pid":"9d8cd4fcc9a09dbc720558fd8e56d9ce3346d899","tid":59913,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"好掛住好掛住一個人<br />\n而家晚晚發夢都見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d1ecd1a32c0915240cfd53c0cbb9ef7c33d26","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係，會笑，但好似好耐未試過真正開心過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兄台 你有冇人生目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇，成日問自己想點，想搵樣興趣想搵個目標，但始終都唔知自己最想做乜。<br />\n<br />\n點解第二條問題就會問有冇人生目標？係好易睇得出？定係你識解夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘅 我覺得如果一個人係有目標(或者夢想)嘅 而佢係為自己嘅目標去奮鬥緊 咁係一件開心嘅事 就算過程係幾辛苦都好<br />\n但係香港呢個地方 好少人可以揾到自己嘅目標同夢想 因為係現實嘅香港 根本冇空間俾你發夢 連生活都有困難 好多人生存都唔知係為咩 所以好多人唔開心<br />\n試下揾日得閒 去一個你鐘意嘅地方 熄左電話 發下夢 可能令你嘅人生有收穫呢"},{"pid":"e0a9a6a824ba71538d694da1ef1d6dd60f3e9c6c","tid":59913,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兄台 你有冇人生目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇，成日問自己想點，想搵樣興趣想搵個目標，但始終都唔知自己最想做乜。<br />\n<br />\n點解第二條問題就會問有冇人生目標？係好易睇得出？定係你識解夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘅 我覺得如果一個人係有目標(或者夢想)嘅 而佢係為自己嘅目標去奮鬥緊 咁係一件開心嘅事 就算過程係幾辛苦都好<br />\n但係香港呢個地方 好少人可以揾到自己嘅目標同夢想 因為係現實嘅香港 根本冇空間俾你發夢 連生活都有困難 好多人生存都唔知係為咩 所以好多人唔開心<br />\n試下揾日得閒 去一個你鐘意嘅地方 熄左電話 發下夢 可能令你嘅人生有收穫呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有 唔洗成日逼自己諗自己想點 用壓力諗出嚟嘅[想點]係冇咁好 <br />\n到有一日 你突然諗到自己想點 你已經超越左好多香港人"},{"pid":"d8d570af9dca36029cd33fd597222ac881b6c36b","tid":59913,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過夢見有人傷害我身邊既人 唔記得屋企人定女朋友<br />\n跟住我綁架左佢 <br />\n用鉗鉗晒佢手指腳指甲佢<br />\n敲碎晒佢棚牙<br />\n將佢兩粒睾丸用兩支篤魚蛋既牙簽釘係左右兩邊大脾到<br />\n跟住捉埋佢女朋友逼佢含到爆嗰下要條女咬爛佢吞落肚 <br />\n唔係就殺左條女佢<br />\n<br />\n跟住就醒左覺得勁恐怖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解可以發啲咁恐怖嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c548808bca5f21d1990f60069c031ba6ff17dcb","tid":59913,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲男性嘅眼神真係好正 好有魅力 好吸引 我幻想到 我真係幻想到</blockquote><br />\n溫柔到我想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜之後再冇夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係未來等緊你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6a1fa1d681b330b00a4d0727936eefbe93379c","tid":59913,"uid":70311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"同銘皇星錫咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c160c0a39380d2eb0257a6e1a40e959e86d5b85f","tid":59913,"uid":57531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWrifmDARrNjrrWHjrqjwxvLN9nKBQdsdJ69RdzTKrXj7?filename=5jz5ZnS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jz5ZnS.jpg&h=38191420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09f68cff59a01e6d23835c7404cdd55a4c736faa","tid":59913,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗰陣老豆喺我考試嗰陣走咗，我冇機會去醫院探佢、見佢最後一面<br />\n佢走咗之後我好嬲自己，因為喺佢走之前嗰個父親節，我同佢一齊睇父親節廣告，我想同佢講我愛你，我知機會可能不多，但我最後都係冇做到，我一生嘅遺憾就係冇得陪住佢行最後嗰段路同埋唔夠膽表達愛意<br />\n之後過咗一排我發夢見到佢，我即刻攬到佢實一實，係溫暖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心諗居然喺夢到feel到體溫，然後喊醒咗<br />\n之後所有有佢嘅夢我都記得</blockquote><br />\n好sad...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好耐之前發夢都試過攬住一個我唔可以再攬住嘅人 然後喊醒 嗰日個夢發左好耐 我同佢傾左好耐計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我俾你攬下啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01faf0b8398a50b34b7b7ff903a09aa8e4fc809c","tid":59913,"uid":63127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"係茶餐廳同一個陌生人對望，<br />\n忽然佢個人自焚， 然後撲埋我度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79528c256552eb0db098fedc1c2aaa51f4f8d1f","tid":59913,"uid":3018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"細個試過發一個夢，自己變到好細，姐係好似蟻咁樣，週圍好多好高既草，跟著我行到去一個建築物，入面3，4個人係我同伴（現實應該未見過既人），我同果班人一齊出去冒險，最記得係去到一條河流，要用樹葉過去，其中一個同伴失手跌落水仲漂走，我救番佢就醒左，好似因為心跳加速醒。<br />\n之後我諗番會發呢個夢，應該係睇過一套卡通片，話男主角比隻蟻變做隻蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8056124cf700c7f54c9b6a62295ce57eeddfcf0","tid":59913,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"唔知點解發親春夢都係未射就醒左"},{"pid":"3e0c50079a64e341a7790b23128509bd56ebe7a1","tid":59913,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"同中學級花做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c4b322fdf5d5617aa825d8df09ebefdb97dc32","tid":59913,"uid":3910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"前面架旅遊巴抄車<br />\n所有人死晒<br />\n去汁人地啲眼球拎返屋企炸黎食"},{"pid":"fa82bba535dd14a709e7c9e21b0f61b574326af0","tid":59913,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前面架旅遊巴抄車<br />\n所有人死晒<br />\n去汁人地啲眼球拎返屋企炸黎食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e7e8e893ca5d27ae2ed0e34c87a83d0342f929","tid":59913,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前面架旅遊巴抄車<br />\n所有人死晒<br />\n去汁人地啲眼球拎返屋企炸黎食</blockquote><br />\n我最多都係用化屍粉殺左十零廿個路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺完就開開心心繼續散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}